title: [Quit Stallin', Silver Scales]
[Quit Stallin', Iron Maiden]
description: Sturdy iron fixtures are placed throughout the space, giving a rugged feel to this spacious display room.  Spread across one section of flooring is a layer of clean straw bedding.  A scale-traced blackened hay rack has been affixed to some rough-hewn wall planks, beside a sturdy hook dangling a dragon-etched silver feed pail.  A display table resting in the straw shows off the appearance of a plum-painted silver watering trough.  Prominently nailed near the entrance is a large parchment notice.
